headline: Did the Howard Street Tunnel Expansion Just Shift CSX's (CSX) Investment Narrative?
summary: CSX Corporation recently announced the re-opening of the expanded Howard Street Tunnel, a historic US$450 million infrastructure project designed to modernize freight rail transportation along the East Coast and enable double-stacked intermodal trains through Baltimore. This upgrade addresses a longstanding supply chain constraint in the region, opening new opportunities for freight shippers and increasing the Port of Baltimore's business by an estimated 160,000 containers annually.
